verbs.description: President Donald Trump [V: will] lay a wreath at Arlington National Cemetery on Monday to honor fallen service members . He is expected to head to the US military cemetery after spending much of the holiday weekend golfing and tweeting attacks aimed at the special counsel 's investigation , Democrats and the press .
